 One-time colleague of slain Teasers boss Lolly Jackson and co-author of the book entitled ‘Lolly Jackson’, Sean Newman, is now working on another gripping thriller – this time into the murky world of Mirror Trading International (MTI), which was rated by Chainalysis as the largest crypto scam in the world in 2020. He shares his experience with Jackson and Radovan Krejcir, as well as his research into the MTI story. Read:
